</div></section>

<!-- WINNERS & LOSERS -->
<section class="dsec" id="winners"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="sec-head"><div><div class="eyebrow">The regime, scored</div><h2>Winners &amp; losers.</h2></div></div>
  <p class="lead">Who a firm dollar, restrictive real rates, and the oil shock help — and who they squeeze.</p>
  <div class="wl3">
    <div class="wl-lane wl-win"><div class="wl-h">Winners</div>{wlLane('win').map((r) => (<div class="wl-item"><b>{r[1]}</b><span>{r[2]}</span></div>))}</div>
